<div class="zm-item" data-type="Answer">
<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/290568047/answer/471914026" data-id="26847724" data-za-element-name="Title">
IPO 被否原因有哪些，被否后会再次申请吗？
</a></h2>
<div tabindex="-1" class="zm-item-answer "
itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Answer"
data-aid="115872334"
data-atoken="471914026"
data-collapsed="0"
data-created="1534568512"
data-deleted="0"
data-isowner="0"
data-helpful="True"
data-copyable="0"
data-zop
>
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/290568047/answer/471914026">
<meta itemprop="answer-id" content="115872334">
<meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="471914026">
<a class="zg-anchor-hidden" name="answer-115872334"></a>

<div class="zm-item-vote">
<a class="zm-item-vote-count js-expand js-vote-count" href="javascript:;" data-bind-votecount>43</a>
</div>

