<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/22596057/answer/499117219" data-id="1219069" data-za-element-name="Title">
同为状元控卫的沃尔和欧文谁现在更强？
</a></h2>
<div tabindex="-1" class="zm-item-answer "
itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Answer"
