<span title="NBA华盛顿奇才队球员" class="bio">
NBA华盛顿奇才队球员
</span>
</span>
</div>

<div class="zm-item-vote-info" data-votecount="453">


<span class="answer-tag">
<span class="text">收录于 </span>


<span class="text">编辑推荐</span>



</span>


<span class="zg-bull text">•</span><span class="voters text"><a href="#" class="more text"><span class="js-voteCount">453</span>&nbsp;人赞同</a></span>


