<h2><a class="post-link" href="https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/46980536" data-za-element-name="Title">视频评测：《刺客：奥德赛》——橙色史诗级大刷子</a></h2>
<div tabindex="-1" class="zm-item-feed zm-item-post" data-type="p">
<link itemprop="url" href="https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/46980536">
<meta itemprop="post-id" content="9502175">
