<div class="zm-item" data-type="Answer">
<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/33612748/answer/424471727" data-id="5651673" data-za-element-name="Title">
建筑的参数化设计是将来的必然趋势吗？
</a></h2>
<div tabindex="-1" class="zm-item-answer "
itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Answer"
data-aid="107245620"
data-atoken="424471727"
data-collapsed="0"
data-created="1529753111"
data-deleted="0"
data-isowner="0"
data-helpful="True"
data-copyable="1"
data-zop
>
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/33612748/answer/424471727">
<meta itemprop="answer-id" content="107245620">
<meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="424471727">
<a class="zg-anchor-hidden" name="answer-107245620"></a>

