<div class="zm-item" data-type="Answer">
<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/297384905/answer/510585680" data-id="28362171" data-za-element-name="Title">
为什么有的企业经营性现金流连续几年都是负数，而利润却是连年增长？
</a></h2>
<div tabindex="-1" class="zm-item-answer "
itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Answer"
data-aid="122903764"
data-atoken="510585680"
data-collapsed="0"
data-created="1539518404"
data-deleted="0"
data-isowner="0"
data-helpful="True"
data-copyable="0"
data-zop
