<div class="zm-item" data-type="Answer">
<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/287392358/answer/499499617" data-id="26142158" data-za-element-name="Title">
现在的律师人数饱和了吗？
</a></h2>
<div tabindex="-1" class="zm-item-answer "
itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Answer"
data-aid="120887190"
data-atoken="499499617"
data-collapsed="0"
