<div class="zm-item-rich-text expandable js-collapse-body" data-resourceid="2054020" data-action="/answer/content" data-author-name="阿兹皮利奎塔" data-entry-url="/question/24679870/answer/513946880">

<textarea hidden class="content">&lt;p&gt;Thanks for inviting. I'd also like to thank ASP for translation.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;First of all, I want to pick my national team mate Xavi Hernandez. I'm so glad to play with him and to pass him the ball. The way he thinks about football, he controls the ball and vision that he has are quite amazing.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-fb463d5462f859945ed5baeb22b2a17a_b.jpg&quot; data-caption=&quot;&quot; data-size=&quot;normal&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;594&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;406&quot; data-default-watermark-src=&quot;https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-f6112767efa152787890a4bb57114523_b.jpg&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;594&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-fb463d5462f859945ed5baeb22b2a17a_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p&gt;And the other one is my Chelsea teammate Eden Hazard, an excellent player who is able to change the game at any moment. He has the wonderful ability to change speed, master the progress of the game and also score goals at different situation. He is still very young and I do believe that he can improve further.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-a24241ad111410ce23fa143d9312f6df_b.jpg&quot; data-caption=&quot;&quot; data-size=&quot;normal&quot; data-rawwidth=&quot;800&quot; data-rawheight=&quot;450&quot; data-default-watermark-src=&quot;https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-f61f13d5711b2b15cb29e919c2eb5a72_b.jpg&quot; class=&quot;origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb&quot; width=&quot;800&quot; data-original=&quot;https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-a24241ad111410ce23fa143d9312f6df_r.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;谢谢邀请，也谢谢 &lt;a class=&quot;member_mention&quot; href=&quot;//www.zhihu.com/people/6ab20306a1f460e3f1457004b63736a9&quot; data-hash=&quot;6ab20306a1f460e3f1457004b63736a9&quot; data-hovercard=&quot;p$b$6ab20306a1f460e3f1457004b63736a9&quot;&gt;@聚星动力&lt;/a&gt; 的朋友的翻译。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;首先我想选我的国家队队友哈维。我非常开心能够跟他一起踢球。他对足球的见解，他控球的方式，以及他在场上的视野，都令人惊叹。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;另外一个人选，我想选我的切尔西队友艾登-阿扎尔。他是一个可以在任何时刻改变比赛的球员，他能够控制场上的局面，能在各种情况下进球，还有着极为出众的变速能力。而且，他还很年轻，我确信，他还有很大的进步空间。&lt;/p&gt;</textarea>


<div class="zh-summary summary clearfix">
<img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-b4006bd81ca8293fb0999a8a71710287_200x112.jpg" data-caption="" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="594" data-rawheight="406" data-watermark="watermark" data-original-src="v2-b4006bd81ca8293fb0999a8a71710287" data-watermark-src="v2-fb463d5462f859945ed5baeb22b2a17a" data-private-watermark-src="v2-f6112767efa152787890a4bb57114523" data-tags="politic" class="origin_image inline-img zh-lightbox-thumb" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-b4006bd81ca8293fb0999a8a71710287_r.jpg">
Thanks for inviting. I'd also like to thank ASP for translation.First of all, I want to pick my national team mate Xavi Hernandez. I'm so glad to play with him and to pass him the ball. The way he thinks about football, he controls the ba…

