<div class="zm-item" data-type="Answer">
<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/297994185/answer/513586393" data-id="28497483" data-za-element-name="Title">
明明现在用的微积分符号都是莱布尼茨发明的，为什么都说牛顿更伟大？
</a></h2>
<div tabindex="-1" class="zm-item-answer "
itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Answer"
data-aid="123449981"
data-atoken="513586393"
data-collapsed="0"
data-created="1539876970"
data-deleted="0"
data-isowner="0"
data-helpful="True"
data-copyable="0"
data-zop
>
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/297994185/answer/513586393">
<meta itemprop="answer-id" content="123449981">
<meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="513586393">
<a class="zg-anchor-hidden" name="answer-123449981"></a>

<div class="zm-item-vote">
<a class="zm-item-vote-count js-expand js-vote-count" href="javascript:;" data-bind-votecount>282</a>
</div>

